.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, may, march, november
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep, jazz, r&b
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the fan of d&b is between the person watching western movies and the fan of r&b##2
6. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Birthday          | march    | may  | november  | september |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | action | romance |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | d&b     | r&b    | dubstep |

