.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, ferret, hamster, hedgehog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's sport is cycling##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person who's sport is cycling and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving  |
| Pet   | hamster | ferret       | hedgehog | guinea-pig |
| Sport         | handball   | cycling      | lacrosse | golf       |

