The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, spy, superhero
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, oliveros, baccarat, prince
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the game-smoker is between the oliveros-smoker and the person eating tomato##2
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
5. the game-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating tomato is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | tomato  | cabbage   | lemon    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | spy     | superhero | disaster |
| Cigar   | baccarat   | prince | game | oliveros   |

