.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, broccoli, lime, pomegranate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, action, family, superhero
4 different pets are kept: bird, horse, mouse, pony
1. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
4. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
5. the person eating broccoli is between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
6. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating apple##1
8. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | lime    | broccoli    | apple  | pomegranate |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | action | time-travel | family      |
| Pet     | horse   | bird        | pony   | mouse       |

 